title: Snot - get some
description:
Snot is an American rock band from Santa Barbara, California. Formed in 1995, their musical style is a fusion of punk, funk and metal. The band released studio album Get Some with founding vocalist Lynn Strait in 1997 and disbanded after his death in 1998. In 2008, Snot reformed in the original lineup with new vocalist, comprising vocalist Tommy Vext, guitarists Mike Doling and Sonny Mayo, bassist John Fahnestock and drummer Jamie Miller.
